Package HdbOfficer

Class HdbOfficer

java.lang.Object
Users.User
Applicant.Applicant
HdbOfficer.HdbOfficer
public class HdbOfficer extends Applicant
Represents an HDB Officer, extending the Applicant class. The officer manages residential and team applications, maintains a blacklist, and handles project assignments.
